        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "The handle, chain, and spiked ball of this *+1 striking corrosive flail* are all made of iron so rusted that the weapon appears nonfunctional at first glance. On Strikes against a creature that's primarily made of metal, it gains the deadly d10 trait.",
